### 3. ASCII-SystemÃ¼bersicht

```
+-------------------+        TLS 1.3        +-------------------+
|  Client (App/Web) |  <------------------>  |  API Gateway (/v1)|
+---------+---------+                        +----+--------------+
          |                                        |
          | OAuth2/OIDC                            | gRPC/HTTP
          v                                        v
+---------+---------+                        +-----+--------------+
|  Privacy Engine   |                        |  Case Service     |
|  (anon, k-anon)   |                        |  (CRUD Cases)     |
+---------+---------+                        +-----+--------------+
          |                                        |
          v                                        v
+---------+---------+                        +-----+--------------+
|  Ledger Service   |----------------------->|  TRUTH Audit Node |
|  (writeoff, etc.) |   append-only feed     |  (WORM, verify)   |
+-------------------+                        +-------------------+
```

