### 10. Deployment-Profile (konkretisiert)
- Minimal: 1 API (stateless) + 1 Storage (encrypted) + 1 TRUTH Node.
- Standard: 2 API (HA) + 2 Storage (replication) + 1 TRUTH + 1 Privacy Engine.
- Hardenings: HTTPS only, HSTS, CSP, mTLS (service2service), key rotation â‰¤ 180 Tage.

---

### 11. RÃ¼ckwÃ¤rts-/VorwÃ¤rtskompatibilitÃ¤t
- Schema â€žexpand-and-contractâ€œ, `deprecated`-Felder max. 2 Minor-Releases mitfÃ¼hren.
- API-Versionen parallel betreiben (`/v1`, `/v2`), Migrationsfenster dokumentieren.

